[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man stable after accident at Murco site in Milford Haven

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man who was seriously injured in an industrial incident at a former refinery site in Pembrokeshire is in a stable condition and recovering following surgery.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police were called to the old Murco site in Milford Haven on Wednesday just before 09:00 BST .
The man was involved in dismantling the former refinery.
Dyfed-Powys Police said the investigation was in the hands of the Health and Safety Executive.
